                <h2 class="text-justify">Air India Check-ins Policy: </h2>

                <p class="text-justify">
                    The check-in counters for <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/air-india-flights.aspx">Air India Flights</a> open two hours before the flight. Because check-in ends 45 minutes before departure, passengers should arrive 1-2 hours early. Passengers can also check-in online from anywhere in the world, save Srinagar and Jammu, starting 48 hours before their flight and ending 2 hours before their flight. The online feature allows a total of 9 persons to web check-in. Passengers can check in using their smartphones, kiosks, or even telecheck-in (only Executive Class and Frequent flyers from metro cities).
                </p>
